         <div xml:id="alalal-i59988"><!-- l4d33dt1 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-i59988-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i59988-d1e101">
               <cb ed="#Bf" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="19"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i59988-d1e108">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="20"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-i59988-Qd1e112"> Queritur hic de antiquis patribus,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="21"/>etc.</quote>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="22"/>In hac distinctione agitur de diversis
<lb ed="#Bf" n="23"/>conjugii statibus.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i59988-d1e122">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="24"/>Quatuor autem hic queruntur a 
Ma<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="25"/>gistro.
<lb ed="#Bf" n="26"/>Primum est, Quare antiqui aliqui
<lb ed="#Bf" n="27"/>plures uxores habuerunt ?
<lb ed="#Bf" n="28"/>Secundum, de matrimonit 
compara<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="29"/>tione ipsorum ad ccelibatum nove 
gra<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="30"/>ti, ibi, B, <quote xml:id="alalal-i59988-Qd1e139"> Quod vero castitas 
virgina<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="31"/>lis, etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="32"/>Tertio queritur, Utrum licuit unam
<lb ed="#Bf" n="33"/>mulierem habere plures viros, ibi, D,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="34"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-i59988-Qd1e151"> Sed numguid sub lege, etc ? </quote>
               <cb ed="#Bf" n="c"/>
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="35"/>Quarto, tangit statum ceelibum et 
cm<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="36"/>libatus, ibi, iM, <quote xml:id="alalal-i59988-Qd1e159"> Melior est autem 
virgi<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="37"/>nitas mentis quan carnis, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i59988-d1e165">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="38"/>Et haec de divisione sufficiant.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-i59988-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="39"/>Incidunt autem circa principium 
ra<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="40"/>tione primi capituli hic querenda sex.
<lb ed="#Bf" n="41"/>Primum est, An matrimonium sift 
na<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="42"/>turale ?
<lb ed="#Bf" n="43"/>Secundum est, Utrum habere plures
<lb ed="#Bf" n="44"/>uxores sit naturale, vel contra naturam ?
<lb ed="#Bf" n="45"/>Tertium, Utrum unam mulierem 
ha<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="46"/>bere plures viros sit contra naturam vel
<lb ed="#Bf" n="47"/>ordinem nature ?
<lb ed="#Bf" n="48"/>Quartum, Utrum soli libidinosi tune
<lb ed="#Bf" n="49"/>perpetraverunt bigamiam, sicut videtur
<lb ed="#Bf" n="50"/>velle in Littera ?
<lb ed="#Bf" n="51"/>Quintum, Utrum tunc licuit vel 
ali<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="52"/>quando licuit habere concubinam ?
<lb ed="#Bf" n="53"/>Sextum, Qualiter bonum matrimonii
<lb ed="#Bf" n="54"/>quod est sacramentum, salvabatur in
<lb ed="#Bf" n="55"/>matrimoniis antiquorum patrum ?
</p>
